'''Llarn Kristovv''' was a [[Major/Legends|major]] in [[New Republic Intelligence Service|New Republic Intelligence]].

As an Intelligence agent, Kristovv was assigned to be the [[NRI Diplomatic Attache]] to the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[New Republic embassy (Dathomir)|Dathomir Embassy]].

